line_1: Thou never braing't, an' fetch't, an' flisket,
line_2: But thy auld tail thou wad hae whisket,

line_1: Thou never braing't, an' fetch't, an' flisket,
line_2: An' spread abreed thy weel-fill'd brisket,

line_1: Thou never braing't, an' fetch't, an' flisket,
line_2: Till sprittie knowes wad rair't an' risket,
